<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css" />
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindplus/elements@1"
      type="module"
    ></script>

    <title>GA Mafia</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="bg-red-950 py-12 sm:py-16">
      <header class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 z-50">
        <nav
          aria-label="Global"
          class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 lg:px-8"
        >
          <div class="flex lg:flex-1">
            <a href="/" class="-m-1.5 p-1.5">
              <span class="sr-only">Your Missions</span>

              <img src="/image.png" alt="" class="mission-pic1 h-8 w-auto" />
            </a>
          </div>
        </nav>
      </header>
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
          <h2 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-red-400">Instructions</h2>
          <p
            class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-pretty text-white sm:text-5xl lg:text-balance"
          >
            Everything you need to know for the mafia missions
          </p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg/8 text-gray-300">
            Some missions will be solo, paired, or team-based. These
            instructions will help you understand what you need to focus on in
            order to complete your missions.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-4xl">
          <dl
            class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-y-16"
          >
            <div class="relative pl-16">
              <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-white">
                <div
                  class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex size-3 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-red-500"
                ></div>
                Mission Verification
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base/7 text-gray-400">
                You must prove that you completed your missions by contacting
                one of the IAs before starting the mission.
              </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
              <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-white">
                <div
                  class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex size-3 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-red-500"
                ></div>
                Submitting Proof
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base/7 text-gray-400">
                For missions that do not require IA supervision, you can submit
                proof via Slack in the form of an image or video.
              </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
              <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-white">
                <div
                  class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex size-3 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-red-500"
                ></div>
                Time Frame
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base/7 text-gray-400">
                You have approximately 3 months to complete all missions. There
                is no strict deadline for individual missions.
              </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
              <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-white">
                <div
                  class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex size-3 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-red-500"
                ></div>
                Location & Timing
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base/7 text-gray-400">
                All missions must be completed on campus and during official
                working hours.
              </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
              <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-white">
                <div
                  class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex size-3 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-red-500"
                ></div>
                Secrecy Rule
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base/7 text-gray-400">
                Do not reveal that you are part of the Mafia or confess your
                role to anyone.
              </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
              <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-white">
                <div
                  class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex size-3 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-red-500"
                ></div>
                Communication Channel
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base/7 text-gray-400">
                A Mafia Slack group will be created with the IAs for all
                mission-related communication.
              </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
              <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-white">
                <div
                  class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex size-3 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-red-500"
                ></div>
                Focus Rule
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base/7 text-gray-400">
                Missions must not interfere with your classes or distract you
                during sessions.
              </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
              <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-white">
                <div
                  class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex size-3 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-red-500"
                ></div>
                Asking Questions
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base/7 text-gray-400">
                If you have any questions about a mission, contact one of the
                IAs for clarification.
              </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
              <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-white">
                <div
                  class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex size-3 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-red-500"
                ></div>
                Completion Approval
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base/7 text-gray-400">
                A mission is only considered completed once it has been approved
                by an IA.
              </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
              <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-white">
                <div
                  class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex size-3 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-red-500"
                ></div>
                Failure Consequences
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base/7 text-gray-400">
                If you fail 4 or more missions, 3 hints will be revealed to the
                detectives; if you fail 3 missions, 2 hints will be revealed;
                and if you fail 2 missions, 1 hint will be revealed.
              </dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>
      <footer
        class="border-t border-gray-700 py-6 text-center text-sm text-gray-400"
      >
        Created by your favorite IA
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
